INSERT INTO vacancy (id, about, broker, hours, location, posting_date, salary, title, vacancy_number, vacancyurl) VALUES ('57213cf3-36ac-45c0-ba0b-d7e4100f55cc', 'Solution Architect Solliciteer Solliciteer op de website van de werkgever Premium 12 augustus ANWB Are you keen to contribute as a Senior Solution Architect to an inspiring mobile customer journey? At the ANWB App Center, we apply the latest technologies to develop innovative digital products for millions of users. Waar je aan werkt Working at the ANWB App Center is a unique experience. We set demanding goals but also give you ample opportunity to achieve them. We will never stop challenging ourselves and our stakeholders to create the best possible solutions for our users. There is plenty of room for individual input at the App Center. Your daily tasks are not a mould for you to fit into. Instead, there is enough to be discovered and learned when it comes to app development. Your responsibilities: Design and development of backend/frontend solutions Comunication with other teams and departments Comunication with 3rd parties Help team to make good architectural decisions. Comunicate technical things to non-technical people. Maintain develop our Java applications. Maintain our API Gateway proxies (we use Apigee) Comunicate and create requirements for 3rd party API vendors. Vaardigheden Hebben we een match? You are able to comunicate clearly with non-technical people. You have experience with REST API design and development. You have some exposure to Java/Springboot + databases. You have strong comunication skills. You know specifics of developing backend services for mobile apps. Some experience with native mobile frontend development is nice to have. You are a strong team player and together with your colleagues, you manage to take the team to a higher level. You have professional and intellectual abilities at the BSc level. You are enthusiastic, proactive and you want to change the world! You are a reside